[
  "<h3 class='og-mt-4'>Sistema Flexbox</h3>",
  "<p>Alternativa a Grid para layouts más simples y flexibles.</p>",
  "<h4 class='og-mt-3'>Flex Row (Horizontal)</h4>",
  "<div class='og-flex og-row og-gap-md og-my-2'>",
  "<div class='og-bg-blue-200 og-p-2 og-rounded'>Item 1</div>",
  "<div class='og-bg-blue-500 og-p-2 og-rounded'>Item 2</div>",
  "<div class='og-bg-blue-600 og-p-2 og-rounded og-text-white'>Item 3</div>",
  "</div>",
  "<pre class='og-bg-gray-100 og-p-2 og-rounded' style='overflow-x: auto; font-size: 0.85rem;'><code>&lt;div class='og-flex og-row og-gap-md og-my-2'&gt;\n  &lt;div&gt;Item 1&lt;/div&gt;\n  &lt;div&gt;Item 2&lt;/div&gt;\n  &lt;div&gt;Item 3&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>",
  "<h4 class='og-mt-3'>Flex Column (Vertical)</h4>",
  "<div class='og-flex og-column og-gap-md og-my-2' style='max-width: 300px;'>",
  "<div class='og-bg-blue-200 og-p-2 og-rounded'>Item 1</div>",
  "<div class='og-bg-blue-500 og-p-2 og-rounded'>Item 2</div>",
  "<div class='og-bg-blue-600 og-p-2 og-rounded og-text-white'>Item 3</div>",
  "</div>",
  "<h4 class='og-mt-3'>Flex con Wrap</h4>",
  "<div class='og-flex og-wrap og-gap-sm og-my-2'>",
  "<button class='btn btn-primary'>Botón 1</button>",
  "<button class='btn btn-secondary'>Botón 2</button>",
  "<button class='btn btn-primary'>Botón 3</button>",
  "<button class='btn btn-secondary'>Botón 4</button>",
  "<button class='btn btn-primary'>Botón 5</button>",
  "<button class='btn btn-secondary'>Botón 6</button>",
  "</div>",
  "<h4 class='og-mt-3'>Flex con Alineación Center</h4>",
  "<div class='og-flex og-center og-gap-md og-my-2 og-bg-gray-100 og-rounded' style='min-height: 150px;'>",
  "<div class='og-bg-blue-600 og-p-2 og-rounded og-text-white'>Centrado Total</div>",
  "</div>",
  "<h4 class='og-mt-3'>Flex Space Between</h4>",
  "<div class='og-flex og-between og-gap-md og-my-2 og-bg-gray-100 og-p-2 og-rounded'>",
  "<div class='og-bg-green-600 og-p-2 og-rounded og-text-white'>Inicio</div>",
  "<div class='og-bg-green-600 og-p-2 og-rounded og-text-white'>Final</div>",
  "</div>",
  "<h3 class='og-mt-4'>Ejemplo Real: Dashboard</h3>",
  "<p>Combinando grids, gaps y espaciado para crear un dashboard.</p>",
  "<div class='og-grid og-cols-4 og-gap-md og-my-3'>",
  "<div class='alert alert-info alert-filled og-border-l-4 og-border-blue-600 og-rounded-lg'>",
  "<h2 class='og-text-blue-700 og-mb-0'>1,234</h2>",
  "<small class='og-text-gray-600'>Total Users</small>",
  "</div>",
  "<div class='alert alert-success alert-filled og-border-l-4 og-border-green-600 og-rounded-lg'>",
  "<h2 class='og-text-green-700 og-mb-0'>$45.2k</h2>",
  "<small class='og-text-gray-600'>Revenue</small>",
  "</div>",
  "<div class='alert alert-warning alert-filled og-border-l-4 og-border-yellow-600 og-rounded-lg'>",
  "<h2 class='og-text-yellow-700 og-mb-0'>89</h2>",
  "<small class='og-text-gray-600'>Orders</small>",
  "</div>",
  "<div class='alert alert-danger alert-filled og-border-l-4 og-border-red-600 og-rounded-lg'>",
  "<h2 class='og-text-red-700 og-mb-0'>12</h2>",
  "<small class='og-text-gray-600'>Issues</small>",
  "</div>",
  "</div>",
  "<div class='og-grid og-cols-2 og-gap-md og-my-3'>",
